    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Members of an order containing over 680,000 living species of insects that develop wings inside the body and undergo an elaborate metamorphosis involving a pupal stage.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
